<body>
	<style>
		.item {
			margin-top: 25%;
		}

		.but {
			width: 50%;
			height: 45px;
			margin-bottom: 20px;
			background-color: rgb(25, 17, 12);
			color: white;
			font-family: monospace;
			text-align: center;
			border-radius: 18px;
		}

		video {
			width: 1100px;
		}
	</style>
	@model Assignment.Models.Product;
	<form action="@Url.Action("ShowCart","Home",new {  ProductId=Model.ID  } )" method="post">
	<div class="container" >
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-md-6">
				<img src="/images/@Model.Image" alt="" width="100%">
			</div>
			<div class="col-md-6">
				<div class="thumbnail">
					<div class="item">

						<h1>@Model.Name</h1>
						<h2>@Model.Price</h2>
						
					
						
						<button class="but">
							<i id="mua" class="fa-sharp fa-solid fa-basket-shopping"></i>
							<a>Mua</a>
						</button>
						<button class="but" type="submit">
							<i id="them" class="fa-solid fa-cart-shopping"></i>
							<a href style="text-decoration:none ; color:white">Thêm vào giỏ hàng</a>
						</button>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	</form>
	<div class="container">
		The LVxYK Keepall 50 was created as part of the inspired new Louis Vuitton
		x Yayoi Kusama collection. Outside, it’s embellished with one of the
		eminent Japanese artist’s best-known images, dating from 1993: a
		psychedelic flower interlaced with her emblematic dots, symbolizing the
		ephemeral nature of life and the infinity of time. Inside, it features an
		exclusive LVxYK signature, transforming a classic bag into an artistic
		collector’s item.

		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-md-8">
				<div class="thumbnail">
					<h1>Product Detail</h1>
					<hr />
					50 x 29 x 23 cm (Length x height x width )
					<li>
						White Taurillon Monogram cowhide with Psychedelic Flower print
					</li>
					<li>Cowhide-leather trim</li>
					<li>polyester</li>
					<li>Cotton and polyester lining</li>
					<li>Palladium-color hardware</li>
					<li>Inside LVxYK signature</li>

					<div class="caption"></div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="col-md-4">
				<div class="thumbnail">
					<div class="caption"></div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<br />
	<div class="container">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-md-12">
				<div class="thumbail">
					<center>
						<video src="https://lv-vod.fl.freecaster.net/vod/louisvuitton/JPJaCakTB3_HD.mp4" width="100%" autoplay loop>
						</video>
					</center>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</body>

</html>